long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing "CarsNew Tab" - a Chrome extension designed for car enthusiasts. Enjoy a new car wallpaper every time you open a new tab, featuring a wide range of stunning cars. Personalize your browsing experience with various categories, including Supercars, Muscle Cars, and Vintage Classics. Elevate your browsing with "CarsNew Tab", where every tab is a captivating journey into the world of cars.

By clicking "Add to Chrome" I accept and agree to install the "CarsNew Tab" Chrome extension and hereby agree to set the Chrome New Tab to that provided by the service and the Privacy policy and Terms of Use. The search results will be provided by Microsoft Bing.
